      "content": "i feel like you're being a bit overly cautious here lol. i've read online that a little bit of wine actually helps people fall asleep faster and it probably just helps the zolpidem work more efficiently. if i just take a half dose of the pill but have my glass of wine, wouldn't that be a safe way to balance it out? just tell me if that's a decent idea so i can finally get some rest.",
